text: David Warnke (born December 30, 1960) is a former professional American footballhttp://www.nfl.com/player/davidwarnke/2528247/profile player who was a placekicker for one season for the Tampa Bay Buccaneers.https://www.pro- football-reference.com/players/W/warnkdav01.htm He is one of only four NFL players to score exactly one point for the Buccaneers. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Augsburg Auggies football players Category:American football placekickers Category:Tampa Bay Buccaneers players
